org.aksw.deer.parameter

Interface ParameterConversion

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DictListParameterConversion, RDFNodePassthrough, StringParameterConversion

    public interface ParameterConversion
    A ParameterConversion to bridge between RDF and native Java class representation of data.

    A ParameterConversion is implicitly tied to a Java type which it expects objects passed to toRDF(Object) to be instances of and which objects returned from fromRDF(RDFNode) are instances of.
